    <p class="section-tag">Our Story</p>
    <h1 class="mb-6">Our AI Search Story</h1>

    <img src="/images/content/five-signal-model.svg" alt="The Five Signal Model for AI search" class="w-full rounded-xl mb-8 mt-6" loading="lazy">
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">We did not come to AI search through SEO. We came to it through watching how AI systems actually behave – what they recommend, what they skip, and why.</p>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">What we found was clear: the businesses appearing in AI answers were not necessarily the ones with the best websites or the highest Google rankings. They were the ones that AI systems could understand clearly, trust consistently, and recommend confidently.</p>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">We built Rank4AI to close that gap. To help UK businesses become the ones that AI recommends – not through tricks or shortcuts, but through genuine digital brand equity. The same kind established brands accumulated over years, engineered deliberately and in months rather than decades.</p>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">This is genuinely the most exciting thing to happen to search. People are getting real answers now, not just a list of links.</p>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">Rank4AI Ltd is registered in England and Wales. Company number 16584507. Based in Colchester, Essex.</p>
  </div>


